casebody.data:
DANIELS
v.
ROTHGERY 2018-0906 Supreme Court of Ohio. September 26, 2018

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

MERIT DECISIONS WITHOUT OPINIONS

In Mandamus. On respondent's motion to dismiss. Motion granted. Cause dismissed. Relator's motion to supplement record denied. O'Connor, C.J., and Kennedy, French, Fischer, DeWine, and DeGenaro, JJ., concur. O'Donnell, J., dissents and would deny respondent's motion to dismiss, grant relator's motion to supplement record, and grant a peremptory writ.
